txt.en: You've collected enough supplies for the Kafagur hunters.\n\nYou should return to Rúkbag at Kafagur.
'Many thanks. The fresh supplies will help us enormously during these trying times.'
Hunt acid drakelings in Jeb Lipha ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Rúkbag has asked you to hunt in Jeb Lipha, east of Kafagur.\n\nThe hunters require phials of acid from drakelings, as well as hide from the larger drakes.
Hunt drakes in Jeb Lipha for hide ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Hunt drakelings in Jeb Lipha for phials of acid ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

'We need more phials of acid and drake hide for our equipment, but we lack enough uninjured hunters able to travel east to Jeb Lipha.\n\n'If you're willing, would you hunt in our stead? It's easier to procure acid from the drakelings, but the best and toughest hide comes from the larger drakes.'
There aren't enough uninjured hunters in Kafagur able to hunt for fresh supplies in Jeb Lipha.
